@startuml
title Flow F-005: Security auditing

participant "Policy Boundary" as PolicyBoundary
participant "Business Service" as BusinessService
participant "Audit Service" as AuditService
database "Audit Repository" as AuditRepository

PolicyBoundary -> BusinessService: Execute sensitive action
BusinessService --> PolicyBoundary: Success or failure outcome
PolicyBoundary -> AuditService: Create audit record
AuditService -> AuditRepository: Persist actor/action/target/time/context
AuditRepository --> AuditService: Stored
@enduml
